    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-1a' );" name="004-1a" class="pb">[004-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　毛詩名物解卷四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:220'>　　　　　　　　　　宋　蔡　卞　集解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='220:225'>　釋草</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='225:246'>　　　荇　　蔞　　菅　　菼　　瓠　　葑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='246:267'>　　　菲　　苓　　唐　　諼　　蒲　　蓷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='267:288'>　　　藚　　蓍　　鷊　　臺　　緑　　菫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='288:309'>　　　蓄　　蓼　　蒹　　葭　　茹　　藘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='309:335'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-1b' );" name="004-1b" class="pb">[004-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='335:350'>　　　蕨　　蘩　　蘿　　莪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='350:355'>　　荇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='355:378'>荇菜謂之茆芥順陽而長本係隂而固有清潔不可陷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='378:401'>溺之徳故以況淑女以薦神明泮水曰思樂泮水薄采</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='401:424'>其茆蓋僖公有教養之善而有所教者其卒有髙明光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='424:447'>大之徳也一章言薄采其芹行足以事人也三章言薄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='447:470'>采其茆徳足以事鬼神也徳足以事鬼神然後可以燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='470:481'>飲食錫難老屈羣醜矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='481:507'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-2a' );" name="004-2a" class="pb">[004-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='507:512'>　　蔞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='512:535'>蔞野草之賤者所以喻漢上遊女孤直而異於衆木故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='535:558'>雖生於中田原野之間與薪相錯而翹翹可辨矣賢不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='558:581'>肖之相别亦何以異於此哉文王之道被於周南則雖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='581:600'>漢上之游女無曲從之志而特可以禮求也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='600:605'>　　菅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='605:628'>菅物之柔忍者也其理白其形柔故謂之茅制而用之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='628:651'>故謂之菅茅自然之潔白故以之共祭祀菅漚畜而柔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='651:677'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-2b' );" name="004-2b" class="pb">[004-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='677:701'>忍故以之爲索綯祭祀明徳之事大徳足以事鬼神者妻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='701:725'>道也索綯賤用之物小惠足以尸鄙事者妾道也幽王黜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='725:749'>申后而立襃姒下國化之以妾為妻以孽代宗而白華之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='749:773'>詩作而刺之曰白華菅兮白茅束兮白華漚而為菅則菅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='773:800'>者<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span>使然之致用而爲綯則卑且勞矣故以譬孽妾茅自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='800:824'>然之正體藉地以祭則靜且安矣故以譬宗嫡不以賤妨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='824:848'>貴不以貴廢賤者人道也不以茅棄菅不以菅害茅者天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='848:872'>道也詩曰英英白雲露彼菅茅露者天之所以成物菅之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='872:898'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-3a' );" name="004-3a" class="pb">[004-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='898:916'>之賤茅之貴二者皆有以成況易其位哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='916:921'>　　菼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='921:944'>菼萑也萑之始生者也萑薍也萑之成體者也蒹蒹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='944:967'>萑之未秀者也菼小於萑萑小於蒹菼青而後潔故曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='967:997'>毳衣如菼白露降然後<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0841' title='KR0841' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0841.png'/>可以爲用故也七月言八月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='997:1015'><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0841' title='KR0841' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0841.png'/>葦未用也故聲從完</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1015:1020'>　　瓠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1020:1043'>瓠甘而可食附物而生者也以其可食而非養人之大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1043:1069'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-3b' );" name="004-3b" class="pb">[004-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1069:1092'>者況在下之賢人無所附則實不成詩曰南有樛木甘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1092:1115'>瓠纍之樛木所以接下者非使然也故以況至誠之君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1115:1138'>子甘瓠之所以纍上者亦自然也故以況在下之賢人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1138:1161'>君子之接下賢人之附上豈有意於彼我之分所能爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1161:1165'>之哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1165:1172'>　　葑　菲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1172:1195'>葑蘆服也苖及下體皆可食而無棄葑者封也卦之於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1195:1218'>土而後盛者也菲芴也蔌必食苖而葑也菲也以下體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1218:1244'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-4a' );" name="004-4a" class="pb">[004-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1244:1267'>爲美故以采葑采菲無以下體菲薄也物之體薄而可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1267:1272'>食者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1272:1277'>　　苓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1277:1300'>苓大苦也所以和百藥之性使之相爲用者也故苓從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1300:1323'>令簡兮曰山有榛隰有苓榛非冝山而不冝隰苓非冝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1323:1346'>隰而不冝山故榛有植於樊棘之内苓或采於首陽之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1346:1369'>巔榛也苓也其生不擇地而美者也猶之賢者無所進</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1369:1376'>而不自得焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1376:1402'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-4b' );" name="004-4b" class="pb">[004-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1402:1407'>　　唐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1407:1430'>唐王女也松枝化而生女蘿之生依乎松故又謂之䝉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1430:1453'>䝉蔽也蔽於松者也桑中之滛亂期於幽逺而志在乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1453:1476'>依所蔽者也故言唐頍弁刺幽王之無親而與諸公興</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1476:1499'>之無附著者也故言女蘿一物而别言之以二者亦此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1499:1503'>意歟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1503:1508'>　　諼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1508:1531'>諼草蘆也喜則形欲動憂則形欲静動所以致其外樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1531:1557'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-5a' );" name="004-5a" class="pb">[004-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1557:1580'>静所以竭其心思樂則有所向而趨明思則有所背而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1580:1603'>趨暗伯兮之室家致思者也故其詩曰焉得諼草言樹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1603:1626'>之背夫載馳之思歸則思渉彼阿丘言采其蝱何以異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1626:1649'>於此也蓋載馳之思在外故欲行以遣其思伯兮之憂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1649:1670'>在内故欲止以忘其憂此二詩之興所以不同也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1670:1675'>　　蒲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1675:1698'>蒲香草也有芬芳之實而生乎澤陂之閒彼澤之陂有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1698:1721'>蒲菡萏是也蓋生於春盛於夏與荷同其榮枯而至於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1721:1747'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-5b' );" name="004-5b" class="pb">[004-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1747:1770'>荷之有華菡萏然於是乎婚姻之時則過至此澤陂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1770:1793'>士女所以滛奔而不可禁也其本作膳又可以爲蔌韓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1793:1816'>奕所謂維筍及蒲是也蒲與筍蔌之至賤者也然以其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1816:1839'>時之所宜獻則不可不備矣公侯燕樂而雖賤者必備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1839:1845'>則貴可知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1845:1850'>　　蓷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1850:1873'>蓷茺蔚也萑也茂於沃壤當夏中和之時旱則乾水則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1873:1896'>死有和平之性此詩人所以況夫婦也中谷有蓷之詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1896:1922'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-6a' );" name="004-6a" class="pb">[004-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1922:1945'>一章言暵其乾矣言生之艱難二章言暵其脩矣脩甚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1945:1968'>於乾況恩衰薄也三章言暵其濕矣濕甚於脩況飢饉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1968:1991'>則相棄也夫蓷隂草也而附於陽生於中谷之寒水則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1991:2018'>非遂性之地也其始也乾其中也脩其卒也濕<span class='krp-note'>疑有所/缺</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2018:2043'>　　藚　蓍　鷊　臺　緑　菫　蓄　蓼<span class='krp-note'>已上/缺</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2043:2050'>　　蒹　葭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2050:2080'>蘆謂之葭其小曰<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0841' title='KR0841' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0841.png'/>荻謂之蒹其小曰蘿其始生之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2080:2103'>　　又謂之薍蒹能兼地於葭所生能侵有之然不如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2103:2129'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-6b' );" name="004-6b" class="pb">[004-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2129:2159'>葭所生之遐不冝下故也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0841' title='KR0841' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0841.png'/>則宜下矣葭能遐假水焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2159:2182'>蒹又謂之兼雖兼地然惡下荻强而葭弱荻髙而葭下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2182:2205'>故謂之荻荻猶逖也蘆秀而蘆蓽可織以爲薄席茨亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2205:2228'>可織雖完而用不如蘆而或析也故音完菼中赤始生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2228:2251'>未黒也而赤故謂之菼其根旁行强揉槃互其行無辨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2251:2274'>矣而又強焉故又謂之薍薍之始生常以無辨惟其強</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2274:2298'>也乃能爲亂詩言毳衣如菼以其赤黒毳𤣥如之言八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2298:2328'>月<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0841' title='KR0841' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0841.png'/>葦以其可辭以其蠶士言蒹葭刺無以保國以其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2328:2354'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-7a' );" name="004-7a" class="pb">[004-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2354:2377'>兼地而遐言葭菼揭揭庶妾上僣以其自下而亂始也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2377:2400'>騶虞以所生乎下言葭行葦以所生在行言葦且葦小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2400:2404'>物也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2404:2411'>　　茹　藘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2411:2434'>茹草者若亨若葅若生食之尤甚變焉皆度所宜以之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2434:2457'>而已故又訓度易所謂㧞茅茹者茅始生可茹者也茹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2457:2480'>藘赤草所染亦赤如此之謂若茈䓞者能已之己其能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2480:2503'>此乎藘生于心色赤南方也方物相見之染如此安能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2503:2529'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-7b' );" name="004-7b" class="pb">[004-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2529:2541'>無慮若茈䓞者何慮之有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2541:2546'>　　蕨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2546:2564'>周秦曰蕨名其始生未有放葉始蕨之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2564:2569'>　　蘩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2569:2592'>髙青均葉蘩日而繇又潔可以生蠶母糸而草之者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2592:2604'>又蘩之醒爲蒿皆髙故也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2604:2609'>　　蘿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2609:2632'>蘿羅生松上如蘿亦羅生而弱又莪謂之蘿科生旁羅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2632:2658'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '004-8a' );" name="004-8a" class="pb">[004-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2658:2661'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2661:2666'>　　莪</span><br/>
